{"article_id":"Um1mK4GNYnAA2C1F","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Longtime Trump adviser Roger Stone was arrested in connection with special counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigation early Friday morning at his home in Florida .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"He was indicted for obstruction , making false statements , and witness tampering .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"You can read the full indictment at this link .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The charges focus on Stone ' s alleged lies to the House Intelligence Committee during 2017 about his statements about and efforts","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"to get in touch with WikiLeaks during the 2016 campaign .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"The indictment also conspicuously mentions","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that \" a senior Trump campaign official was directed to contact Stone \" about what WikiLeaks might have on Hillary Clinton .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The indictment does not , however , attempt to explain","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"why Stone would lie about this","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"or lay out a definitive story","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"about what did happen between Stone and WikiLeaks back then .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Stone also has not been charged with any criminal activity","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"occurring during the campaign .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"The hacking and leaking of Democrats ' emails has long been a central part of the Mueller investigation .","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"Mueller has charged several Russian intelligence officers with the hacking .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"Eventually , WikiLeaks posted many of these emails publicly -","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"the Democratic National Committee ' s in July 2016 , and Clinton campaign chair John Podesta ' s in October 2016 .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"Related","depth":2},{"id":18,"text":"See the moment","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"Roger Stone was arrested by the FBI","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"Various statements by Stone ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"including many public ones ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"raised questions","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"about whether he had some sort of inside knowledge about WikiLeaks or its plans .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"He has denied","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"having any such knowledge","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"- and claimed","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that anything","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"he knew about WikiLeaks","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"came through an intermediary , radio host Randy Credico .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Now Stone has been accused of lying about this to the House Intelligence Committee in 2017 , and trying to tamper with a witness","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"- Credico -","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"so that he would stick to that false story .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"A longtime GOP operative","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"whose reputation for dirty tricks reaches all the way back to Richard Nixon ' s 1972 reelection campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Stone has been an on-and-off adviser to Trump since the mid-1980s .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"That same decade , Stone also co-founded a famous lobbying firm with Paul Manafort .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"When Trump finally did end up running for president in 2015 ,","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Stone was part of his initial campaign team .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"He only lasted a little over a month , though -","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Stone departed the operation in early August","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"after clashing with other staffers .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"However , he remained in Trump ' s orbit and , to some extent , in communication with the candidate himself afterward .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"In fact , he helped engineer Manafort ' s hiring on the campaign .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"As the 2016 general election neared ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Stone frequently spoke about the hacks and leaks of Democratic emails and other documents .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"In August , he praised \" Guccifer 2.0 , \" the online persona","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"taking responsibility","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"for hacking the DNC","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"( Russian intelligence officers reportedly run the account ) .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"He also claimed","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that he had \" communicated \" with Julian Assange , the founder of WikiLeaks ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"which had posted the DNC emails .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"And he repeatedly hinted over the next two months","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that more damaging Clinton material was coming .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Only after the election , though , did we start learning more details about his private communication with both entities .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Roger Stone surreptitiously communicated with both Guccifer 2.0 and WikiLeaks","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"The new indictment claims","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that after July 22 , 2016 , \" a senior Trump Campaign official was directed to contact Stone about any additional releases and what other damaging information","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"\" WikiLeaks \" had regarding the Clinton Campaign . \"","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Around this time","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"- in late July and early August 2016 -","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"Stone also had a set of communications with conservative author Jerome Corsi ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"regarding getting in contact with Assange .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"On July 25 , 2016 , Stone emailed Corsi ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"telling him to \" get to \" Assange in the \" Ecuadorian Embassy in London","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"and get the pending \" WikiLeaks \" emails . \"","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"On July 31 , 2016 , Stone wrote to Corsi","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that Ted Malloch , a Trump campaign adviser , \" should see \" Assange .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"On August 2 , 2016 , Corsi emailed Stone","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"claiming knowledge of Assange ' s plans .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"\" Word is friend in embassy plans 2 more dumps .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"One shortly after I ' m back","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"[ from a trip in Europe ] .","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"2nd in Oct.","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"Impact planned to be very damaging .. \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Corsi continued :","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"\" Would not hurt to start suggesting","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"HRC old , memory bad ,","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"has stroke","depth":17},{"id":80,"text":"-","depth":17},{"id":81,"text":"neither he nor she well .","depth":16},{"id":82,"text":"I expect that much of next dump focus ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"setting stage for [ Clinton ] Foundation debacle . \"","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"Not long afterward , on August 4 , Stone emailed fellow ex-Trump adviser Sam Nunberg ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"\" I dined with Julian Assange last night. \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"( When the email became public long afterward ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Stone said","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"this was just a joke . )","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"The day after that email , on August 5 , Stone penned a Breitbart article","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"in which he took Guccifer ' s story","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"about being a lone hacker","depth":16},{"id":92,"text":"who stole the DNC emails","depth":16},{"id":93,"text":"at face value","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"and argued","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"that Russia probably wasn ' t responsible .","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"He also tweeted","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"that \" Julian Assange is a hero . \"","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Three days later , on August 8 , Stone started publicly claiming to have inside information .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"\" I actually have communicated with Assange , \"","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"\" I believe","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"the next tranche of his documents pertain to the Clinton Foundation","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"but there ' s no telling what the October surprise may be . \"","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"A few days after that , Stone began tweeting at , and eventually DMing with , Guccifer 2.0","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"( who , again , has reportedly been identified as a Russian intelligence officer ) .","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"Some of these DMs later leaked ,","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"leading Stone to post what","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"he claimed","depth":16},{"id":109,"text":"was their full exchange .","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"But the posted messages were mainly friendly chitchat and not particularly substantive .","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"( They are not mentioned in the new indictment . )","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"On August 21 , Stone tweeted an odd prediction :","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"\" Trust me ,","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"it will soon the Podesta ' s time in the barrel .","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"# CrookedHillary . \"","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Many would later point to this","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"- which came months before the Podesta emails became public -","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"and ask","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"whether Stone had advance knowledge of the Podesta email leak .","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"( Stone himself would later claim","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"since this came in the midst of a scandal","depth":16},{"id":123,"text":"surrounding Stone ' s old friend Paul Manafort ' s Ukraine work ,","depth":16},{"id":124,"text":"he was merely predicting","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"\" Podesta ' s business dealings would be exposed . \" )","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"As October began ,","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"Stone took on a new role","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"- as WikiLeaks ' hype man .","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"He again claimed inside knowledge ,","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"saying","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"a \" friend \" of his met with Assange","depth":19},{"id":132,"text":"and learned","depth":19},{"id":133,"text":"\" the mother lode is coming Wednesday. \"","depth":18},{"id":134,"text":"He tweeted :","depth":17},{"id":135,"text":"\" Wednesday @ HillaryClinton is done .","depth":18},{"id":136,"text":"# Wikileaks. \"","depth":18},{"id":137,"text":"And","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"when nothing came on Wednesday ,","depth":18},{"id":139,"text":"Stone tweeted ,","depth":18},{"id":140,"text":"\" Libs","depth":20},{"id":141,"text":"thinking","depth":21},{"id":142,"text":"Assange will stand down","depth":21},{"id":143,"text":"are wishful thinking .","depth":19},{"id":144,"text":"Payload coming .","depth":19},{"id":145,"text":"# Lockthemup. \"","depth":19},{"id":146,"text":"Assange published the Podesta emails two days later .","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Immediately , there were questions","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"about whether the garrulous operative had been involved ,","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"which eventually spurred WikiLeaks to tweet","depth":15},{"id":150,"text":"that the group \" has never communicated with Roger Stone. \"","depth":15},{"id":151,"text":"The Atlantic later reported","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"that Stone DMed the WikiLeaks Twitter account afterward ,","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"complaining","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"that they were \" attacking \" him .","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"\" The false claims of association are being used by the democrats","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"to undermine the impact of our publications , \"","depth":15},{"id":157,"text":"WikiLeaks responded .","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"\" Don ' t go there","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"if you don ' t want us to correct you. \"","depth":15},{"id":160,"text":"Stone shot back :","depth":15},{"id":161,"text":"\" Ha !","depth":16},{"id":162,"text":"The more you ' correct ' me","depth":19},{"id":163,"text":"the more people think","depth":20},{"id":164,"text":"you ' re lying .","depth":20},{"id":165,"text":"Your operation leaks like a sieve .","depth":18},{"id":166,"text":"You need to figure out who your friends are . \"","depth":17},{"id":167,"text":"Stone is actually being charged for his alleged efforts","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"to obstruct the investigation","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"The actual charges against Stone , however , don ' t allege","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"that he committed any crimes during the 2016 campaign .","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"They allege , instead ,","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"that he attempted to obstruct investigations into what happened afterward .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"By 2017 , Stone was putting forward an apparent cover story for whatever actually did happen in 2016 .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"He was insisting","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"that everything","depth":15},{"id":176,"text":"he heard about Assange and WikiLeaks","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"came from just one person","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"- talk radio host Randy Credico ,","depth":16},{"id":179,"text":"whom he called his \" intermediary . \"","depth":16},{"id":180,"text":"So","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"when Stone went to testify before the House Intelligence Committee in closed session in September 2017 ,","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"he stuck to that story .","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"Mueller has indicted Stone on five counts of false statements during that testimony .","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"Stone was also charged with witness tampering for his efforts","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"to get Credico to stick to his false story .","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"\" ' Stonewall it .","depth":16},{"id":187,"text":"Plead the fifth .","depth":18},{"id":188,"text":"Anything","depth":19},{"id":189,"text":"to save the plan ' ...","depth":19},{"id":190,"text":"Richard Nixon , \"","depth":17},{"id":191,"text":"Stone texted Credico at one point .","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"\" If you turned over anything to the FBI","depth":16},{"id":193,"text":"you ' re a fool , \"","depth":16},{"id":194,"text":"he later said .","depth":15},{"id":195,"text":"And eventually ,","depth":15},{"id":196,"text":"when Credico wouldn ' t stick to the story ,","depth":16},{"id":197,"text":"Stone got angrier .","depth":16},{"id":198,"text":"\" You are a rat .","depth":16},{"id":199,"text":"A stoolie .","depth":17},{"id":200,"text":"You backstab your friends , \"","depth":17},{"id":201,"text":"he wrote to Credico in April 2018 .","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"Overall , the indictment makes the case","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"that Stone was lying about the topic of WikiLeaks ,","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"but it does not seem to tell a full story","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"about did happen between Stone , WikiLeaks , and the various intermediaries in 2016 .","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"There ' s ample documentary evidence","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"presented","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"to make the case","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"that Stone ' s story","depth":15},{"id":210,"text":"about Credico being his only contact with Assange","depth":15},{"id":211,"text":"was indeed false .","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"And there are allusions to what Stone was allegedly telling top members of the Trump campaign about WikiLeaks ' plans .","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"But it does not read as any sort of final effort from prosecutors","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"to sum up what did happen back then .","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"That could still come later -","depth":12},{"id":216,"text":"or perhaps they don ' t have sufficient evidence","depth":13},{"id":217,"text":"to show it .","depth":13},{"id":218,"text":"You can read the full indictment below , or at this link .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":437,"left":235,"right":436,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":231,"right":234,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":221,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":0,"right":220,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":222,"right":229,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":227,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":223,"right":226,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":223,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":226,"left":224,"right":225,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":225,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":228,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":232,"right":233,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":232,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":436,"left":17,"right":435,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":435,"left":236,"right":434,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":236,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":434,"left":248,"right":433,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":248,"left":245,"right":247,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":245,"left":239,"right":244,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":237,"right":238,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":20,"right":21,"re